## anonsurf-mac torrc — minimal, transparent-proxy mode

DataDirectory /usr/local/var/lib/anonsurf-mac
RunAsDaemon 1
SocksPort 9050
TransPort 127.0.0.1:9040
DNSPort 127.0.0.1:5353
AutomapHostsOnResolve 1
AutomapHostsSuffixes .onion,.exit
ExitPolicy reject *:*
ClientOnly 1
AvoidDiskWrites 1
Log notice file /usr/local/var/log/anonsurf-mac.log
